title: No. 23 Tech concludes play at Clemson Invitational - VT hokiesports.com
content: No. 23 Tech concludes play at Clemson Invitational  VT hokiesports.com
description: The No. 23 Virginia Tech women's golf team finished 16th at the Clemson Invitational, which concluded Sunday at The Reserve at Lake Keowee (par 72, 6,386 yards).
